title: Firefox audio stuttering
content: i recently noticed that my audio is stuttering a little bit on firefox desktop, expecially on youtube. i already tried the app on incognito mode withou any extension enabled, notthing worked. can be the last Nvidia driver? can be a recent (1 month more or less) mozilla update? can you guys help me please? i ve also formatted the whole pc: nothing
creator: andreagimmobotti

title: How can I create a profile to log into a Mozilla account?
content:
Hello everyone,

I use an unchanging Firefox profile, and would like to synchronize tabs using Firefox Sync. How can I create a profile that logs me into a Mozilla account on startup? I tried using a fixed `signedInUser.json`, but that didn't yield any success.
creator: notcancername
